dcterms:creator: U. Alon
M. Zilberstein
O. Levy
E. Yahav
dcterms:description: A re-split dataset of 11 GitHub projects, containing single methods per example, used for any-code completion tasks. The dataset was filtered to reduce code duplication and contains 1.3M training examples, 10k validation examples, and 20k test examples.
dcterms:title: Java-small dataset

dcterms:creator: M. Brockschmidt
M. Allamanis
A. L. Gaunt
O. Polozov
dcterms:description: A dataset used for restricted code completion tasks, filtering out examples where the targets contain non-primitive types or user-defined functions. It contains 16k training examples, 8k validation examples, and 3k test examples.
dcterms:title: C# dataset (from Brockschmidt et al. (2019))

dcterms:creator: M. Allamanis
M. Brockschmidt
M. Khademi
dcterms:description: An unseen projects test set used for evaluating code representation learning. It contains 30 GitHub projects, broken down into one method per example.
dcterms:title: Allamanis et al. (2018) 'unseen projects test' set
